edu.ucla.sspace.common

Interface DimensionallyInterpretableSemanticSpace<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SemanticSpace
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DependencyVectorSpace, GenericWordSpace

    public interface DimensionallyInterpretableSemanticSpace<T>
extends SemanticSpace
    An interface for SemanticSpace instances that are meaningfully interpretable. In most cases, the dimensions will be understandable by human viewers, but this interface provides support for mapping a dimension to a generic Object for using the description in some programatic manner.
